        joined_path = URI.normalize_path(uri.path)
        joined_query = uri.query

        if uri.authority != nil
          joined_user = uri.user
          joined_password = uri.password

          joined_port = uri.port
          joined_path = URI.normalize_path(uri.path)
          joined_query = uri.query
